claimRewards(address,address).details: Claims the rewards of the specified account for the specified token.

params.to: The address that will receive the rewards.

createVestingSchedule(address,address,ui.details: Creates a vesting schedule for the specified token. The amount of tokens received must be greater than or equal to the specified minimum amount.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to be vested.
params.cliffDuration: The duration of the cliff in seconds.
params.minAmount: The minimum amount of tokens to be received.
params.start: The timestamp at which the vesting will start.
params.vestingDuration: The duration of the vesting in seconds.

returns.index: The index of the vesting schedule.

deposit(address,address,uint256,uint256).details: Deposits the specified amount of tokens to the specified account. The amount of tokens received must be greater than or equal to the specified minimum amount.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to be deposited.
params.minAmount: The minimum amount of tokens to be received.

returns.actualAmount: The actual amount of tokens received.

getNumberOfTokensOf(address).details: Returns the number of tokens staked by the specified account.

returns._0: The number of tokens staked by the specified account.

getNumberOfVestings(address).details: Returns the total number of vestings of the specified token.

returns._0: The total number of vesting schedules of the specified token.

getNumberOfVestingsOf(address,address).details: Returns the number of vestings of the specified token for the specified account.

returns._0: The number of vesting schedules of the specified token for the specified account.

getPendingRewards(address,address).details: Returns the pending rewards of the specified account for the specified token. The reward token is the quote token of the market of the specified token.

returns.pending: The pending rewards of the specified account for the specified token.

getReleasableAmount(address,uint256).details: Returns the amount of tokens that can be released by the specified token at the specified index.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.

returns._0: The amount of tokens that can be released by the specified token at the specified index.

getStakeOf(address,address).details: Returns the stake and locked amounts of the specified account for the specified token.

returns.amount: The stake amount of the specified account for the specified token.
returns.lockedAmount: The locked amount of the specified account for the specified token.

getTokenOf(address,uint256).details: Returns the token staked by the specified account at the specified index. The order of the tokens is not guaranteed.

returns._0: The token staked by the specified account at the specified index.

getTotalStake(address).details: Returns the total staked and total locked amounts of the specified token.

returns.totalLocked: The total locked amount of the specified token.
returns.totalStaked: The total staked amount of the specified token.

getVestedAmount(address,uint256,uint256).details: Returns the total vested amount of tokens by the specified token at the specified index at the specified timestamp.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.
params.timestamp: The timestamp at which the amount of releasable tokens will be calculated.

returns._0: The total vested amount of tokens by the specified token at the specified index at the specified timestamp.

getVestingIndexOf(address,address,uint25.details: Returns the global index of the vesting schedule of the specified token for the specified account at the specified index.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.

returns._0: The global index of the vesting schedule of the specified token for the specified account at the specified index.

getVestingScheduleAt(address,uint256).details: Returns the vesting schedule of the specified token at the specified index.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.

returns._0: The vesting schedule of the specified token at the specified index.

transferVesting(address,address,uint256).details: Transfers the vesting schedule of the specified token at the specified index from the sender to the new beneficiary.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.
params.newBeneficiary: The address of the new beneficiary.

returns._0: The remaining locked amount of tokens.

unlock(address,uint256).details: Unlocks the vested tokens of the specified token at the specified index for the specified account. Anyone can call this function on behalf of the beneficiary as the unlocked tokens are immediately staked.

params.index: The index of the vesting schedule.

withdraw(address,address,uint256).details: Withdraws the specified amount of tokens from the specified account. The amount of tokens withdrawn must be greater than 0.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to be withdrawn.
